body_html:
If you are having this error

ImportError: No module named 'tensorflow.models'

The tensorflow models are not included in tensorflow. You will have to download the tensorflow models zip from GitHub and paste them to the tensorflow folder in python packages.

body:
If you are having this error
```
ImportError: No module named 'tensorflow.models'
```
The tensorflow models are not included in tensorflow. You will have to download the tensorflow models zip from GitHub and paste them to the tensorflow folder in python packages.
